                    <head type="stepTitle" xml:lang="en">Corpus Composition</head>
                    <head type="stepTitle" xml:lang="de">Korpuszusammenstellung</head>
                    <desc type="definition" xml:lang="en">Creation of a corpus, including decision about (1) the corpus type (opportunistic, balanced, etc.) and the criteria of balancedness, (2) the type of annotations (lightweight, multiple layers, inline/standoff, …) and (3) the tagset, i.e. the content of the markup planed. Selection of resources to be included in the corpus (e.g. date range of historical sources, etc.), possibly by reference to the research question.</desc>
                    <desc xml:lang="en" type="terms">
